OL,3,CEverton unveil French striker who
OL,4,Cwants to be known as 'Barry'
OL,6,FEverton have unveiled French striker
OL,7,FThierno Barry as their latest signing.
OL,9,FThe Under-21 international striker has
OL,10,Fsigned for an undisclosed fee, putting
OL,11,Fpen to paper on a four-year contract,
OL,12,Fkeeping him at the Hill Dickinson
OL,13,FStadium until the end of June 2029.
OL,15,FBarry joined Spanish La Liga side
OL,16,FVillarreal last summer from Swiss side
OL,17,FFC Basel, scoring 11 goals ` including
OL,18,Fa hat-trick at Leganes in December `
OL,19,Fto help the Yellow Submarine to a
OL,20,Ffifth-placed finish and qualification
OL,21,Ffor the Champions League.
