OL,6,FBarry ` as he prefers to be called `
OL,7,Ffollowed up by helping France Under-
OL,8,F21s reach the semi-finals of the
OL,9,FEuropean Championships this summer,
OL,10,Fincluding netting a stoppage-time
OL,11,Fwinner against Georgia in the group
OL,12,Fstages.
OL,14,F"I'm very happy," Barry told
OL,15,Fevertontv. "It's very exciting to be
OL,16,Fhere. I just can't wait to start and I
OL,17,Fhope to start very quickly.
