OL,3,CEverton unveil French striker who
OL,4,Cwants to be known as 'Barry'
OL,6,F"Everton is a big club in the Premier
OL,7,FLeague. They have a good history and
OL,8,Fgood players have played here, like
OL,9,FWayne Rooney and Romelu Lukaku. When I
OL,10,Fwas young I liked to watch these
OL,11,Fplayers, now I want to do like these
OL,12,Fplayers who have gone before.
OL,14,F"I had good conversations with the
OL,15,Fmanager. He told me I have the quality
OL,16,Fto play in the Premier League. He
OL,17,Fwants to do good work with me. He
OL,18,Fwants to help me on my road and I felt
OL,19,Fthe sincerity with him so that's why I
OL,20,Fchose to come here as well.
