OL,6,F"For me, it is a dream to play in the
OL,7,FPremier League. I think I proved in my
OL,8,Fcareer so far that I can adapt. For
OL,9,Fexample, last season I went to LaLiga,
OL,10,Fwhich is a top league, and I think I
OL,11,Fhad a good season for my first season.
OL,12,FI'm not scared to play here and do the
OL,13,Fsame."
