OL,3,CEverton unveil French striker who
OL,4,Cwants to be known as 'Barry'
OL,6,FBorn in Lyon of Guinean descent, Barry
OL,7,Fplayed for SC Toulon and FC Sochaux-
OL,8,FMontbeliard youth teams before moving
OL,9,Fto Belgium club Beveren in 2022.
OL,10,FFinishing his maiden campaign with 20
OL,11,Fgoals in Belgium's second tier, a move
OL,12,Fto Swiss Super League side FC Basel in
OL,13,FJuly 2023.
OL,15,FAnother 12 goals followed during 2023-
OL,16,F24, paving the way to his switch to
OL,17,FVillarreal the following summer.
