OL,4,Cwants to be known as 'Barry'
OL,6,F"I think the fans here are, like,
OL,7,Fcrazy people... I like this!" he said.
OL,8,F"I like to score for these people. I
OL,9,Fjust want to play here, score and
OL,10,Fenjoy it with the fans.
OL,12,F"On the pitch I always give 100 per
OL,13,Fcent, I always want to score, I always
OL,14,Fwant to help the team to win. This is
OL,15,Fmy character. For me, this is my meal,
OL,16,Fmy food. When I score, I'm very happy.
OL,17,FI will always give 100 per cent on the
OL,18,Fpitch and try to score goals.
