OL,6,F"The stadium is very big, it's an
OL,7,Famazing stadium, and I'm looking
OL,8,Fforward to seeing the fans in here.
OL,10,F"When the manager came last season, I
OL,11,Fthink he changed a little bit the team
OL,12,Fand I feel this and the new stadium, I
OL,13,Fthink the Club comes with a new
OL,14,Fambition, so I want to play my part in
OL,15,Fthat."
OL,17,FEverton manager David Moyes said: "We
OL,18,Fare delighted to have brought Thierno
OL,19,Fto the Club. We see lots of potential
OL,20,Fand we are hoping for good things from
OL,21,Fhim.
